## 2026-04-05 - Stale generator indicators are not prominent enough
- Added two visibility improvements for stale generators:
  1. **Sub-tab badge**: Yellow pill badge showing stale generator count appears on the "Generators" sub-tab label whenever any generators are stale. Uses `staleGeneratorCount` memoized from `generators.filter(g => g.isStale).length`. Badge styling: `bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900` rounded-full, 14px tall.
  2. **Toast notification on source token edit**: `handleEditorSave` now checks `generatorsBySource.get(savedPath)` to detect if the saved token is a source for any generators. If so, fires an action toast "Source token for N generator(s) changed" with a "Regenerate" button that directly calls `POST /api/generators/:id/run` for each affected generator, then refreshes the generator list. Action toasts persist until explicitly dismissed.

